NG0493:2: dz+wa la ma ta ris tad+ha ya ri da pan tsa tan tra //
NG0493:4: rin po che ral gri 'bar bas rgyud sde spros pa gcod pa zhes bya ba //
NG0493:5: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0493:6: blo cha blo yang blo zab pa'i //
NG0493:7: skal ldan rin chen lta bu la //
NG0493:8: rgyud sde'i spros gcod bshad par bya //
NG0493:9: snying po'i rang bzhin ming med brjod med la //
NG0493:10: rtsal snang yan lag rig po ming btags pas //
NG0493:11: rgyud kyi sde yi spros gcod la //
NG0493:12: don rgyud tshig rgyud gnyis su shes par bya //
NG0493:13: don gyi rgyud kyi rang bzhin ni //
NG0493:14: thog ma med nas tha ma ru //
NG0493:15: rang bzhin rgyud du gnas pa'i rgyud //
NG0493:16: ma bcos ma bslad gzhi mo'i rgyud //
NG0493:20: de ni snying po don gyi rgyud la //
NG0493:21: tshig gi rgyud la rnam gsum ste //
NG0493:22: gzhi yi rgyud dang lam gyi rgyud //
NG0493:23: 'bras bu'i rgyud dang rnam gsum mo //
NG0493:24: gzhi yi rgyud la gnyis yod de //
NG0493:25: khyab pa'i rgyud dang gnas pa'i rgyud //
NG0493:26: khyab pa'i rgyud kyi rang bzhin ni //
NG0493:27: ya tha rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0493:28: ma tha dmyal ba'i 'jigs tshogs su //
NG0493:29: til la mar gyis khyab bzhin du //
NG0493:30: kun la khyab par gnas pa yin //
NG0493:31: gnas pa'i rgyud kyi rang bzhin ni //
NG0493:32: dang po rgyu yis ma bskyed do //
NG0493:33: bar du+u rkyen gyis ma bsgrubs so //
NG0493:34: tha ma gnyen pos mi 'jig go / dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med par gnas //
NG0493:35: de gnyis gzhi yi rgyud du zung *//
NG0493:36: lam gyi rgyud kyi rag bzhin ni //
NG0493:37: rang gzhung gzhan gzhung gnyis kyi rgyud //
NG0493:38: rang gzhung rgyud kyi rgyal po lnga //
NG0493:39: spros gcod sde lnga'i don rgyud bstan //
NG0493:40: gzhan gzhung rgyud kyi rnam grangs te //
NG0493:41: bsam las 'das te re zhig dbye //
NG0493:42: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
NG0493:43: gter rgyud dang ni yongs grags rgyud //
NG0493:44: gter rgyud re zhig mdo tsam dbye //
NG0493:45: rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud la ni //
NG0493:46: mdo rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud dang *//
NG0493:47: rgyun gyi rin po che'o rgyud dang *//
NG0493:48: man ngag gi rin po che rgyas pa'i rgyud do //
NG0493:53: yon tan 'phrin las lnga yin no //
NG0493:54: rgyal po bla gter rgyud la ni //
NG0493:55: rtsa ba'i rgyud rin po che 'khor lo dang *//
NG0493:56: bshad pa'i rgyud rin po che snang byed kyi rgyud dang *//
NG0493:57: rgyud phyi ma'i rgyud rin po che sgron ma 'bar ba'i rgyud dang *//
NG0493:58: yan lag gi rgyud ha dgu dang gnad dgu'i rgyud do //
NG0493:59: rgyud pa bar pa'i rgyud la //
NG0493:60: rtsa ba'i rgyud rgyud kyi rgyal po gser gyi rus sbal dang *//
NG0493:61: bshad pa'i rgyud byang sems thigs pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi rgyud dang *//
NG0493:62: khu byug gsung gi rgyud dang *//
NG0493:65: rus sbal skum gyi rgyud dang *//
NG0493:66: stag mo 'phyongs pa'i rgyud dang lnga'o //
NG0493:67: yan lag gi rgyud bcu gnyis so //
NG0493:70: rin po che gnam rgyud do //
NG0493:71: rin po che spangs pa'i rgyud //
NG0493:72: rin po che 'phrul gyi rgya mdud kyi rgyud do //
NG0493:73: byang gter chen po'i lugs kyis ni //
NG0493:74: rgyud chen rnam pa dgu yin no //
NG0493:75: gter rgyud mdo tsam phye ba'o //
NG0493:76: spyir kri ya'i rgyud lnga brgya bzhugs pa las //
NG0493:77: bsdud pas kri ya brgyad phye ste //
NG0493:78: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dbu'i gtsug nas //
NG0493:79: gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyud dang gcig / ljags las so sor phye ste //
NG0493:80: khri pad+ma 'khyil ba'i rgyud dang gnyis //
NG0493:81: dpung pa gnyis las su na hu ta dpung bzangs phyung ba'i rgyud dang gsum //
NG0493:82: thugs kha nas khro bo rig pa mchog gi rgyud dang bzhi //
NG0493:83: lte ba nas su si ti ka ra phyung ba'i rgyud dang lnga //
NG0493:84: sna las dpal sdom pa'i rgyud phyung ba dang drug
NG0493:85: / zhabs las gshin rje nag po'i rgyud phyung ba
NG0493:86: dang bdun // sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs
NG0493:87: pa la gzungs thams cad phyung ba'i rgyud dang brgyad
NG0493:88: dang bdun // do // rdo rje gtsug tor gyi rgyud chung dun dang *//
NG0493:89: de'i rgyud bsam gtan gyi rgyud do //
NG0493:90: u pa'i theg pa'i rgyud sde la //
NG0493:91: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud sde dang *//
NG0493:92: phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud do //
NG0493:94: sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgyud dang *//
NG0493:95: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le'i rgyud //
NG0493:96: thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud dang *//
NG0493:97: yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po'i rgyud dang *//
NG0493:98: 'phrin las kyi rgyud karma ma le dang *//
NG0493:99: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dang lnga po
NG0493:100: re la yang sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa lnga
NG0493:103: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor dang gcig / dpal mchog dag po'i rgyud dang gnyis //
NG0493:104: glang po chur zhugs kyi rgyud dang gsum mo //
NG0493:105: gsung gi rgyud la'ang gsum ste //
NG0493:106: zla gsang thig le'i rgyud dang *//
NG0493:108: sgron ma brtsegs pa'i rgyud dang gsum mo //
NG0493:109: thugs kyi rgyud la yang gsum ste //
NG0493:112: yid la mi byed dran pa brlag / g.yo med rtsol med sprul sku'o //
NG0493:113: sku gsum dbyer med 'bras ba'i rgyud //
NG0493:114: rgyud kyi rang bzhin rgyun chad med //
NG0493:115: rgyud kyi mtshan nyid bya rtsal med //
NG0493:116: rgyud kyi ngo bo 'gyur ba med //
NG0493:117: rgyud kyi 'bras bu rang gnas yin //
NG0493:118: rin chen ral gri 'bar ba yis //
NG0493:119: gnyis pa'i chos rnams rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:120: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:121: yul sems gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:122: phyi nang gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:123: nga bdag gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:124: spong len gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:125: dgag bsgrub gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:126: rtsol bsgrub gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:127: bzang ngan gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:130: sems kyis phyed tshad rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:131: rig pas btags tshad rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:132: sems chos gnyis kyang rtsad nas gcod //
NG0493:133: rgyud sde ji snyed rtsad nas bcad //
NG0493:136: rgyud sde rtsad nas gcod pa rdzogs so // //
NG0493:137: rgya gar gyi gu ru pad+ma sam b+ha ba las
NG0493:138: // bod kyi lo tsa ba ka ba dpal brtsags kyis bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa'o //
